import { BrowserRouter, Routes, Route, Link } from 'react-router-dom'
import Home from './pages/Home'
import About from './pages/About'

export default function App() {
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
      <nav className="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 bg-slate-900/80 backdrop-blur p-4 z-50">
        <Link to="/" className="text-white mr-4 hover:text-purple-400">Home</Link>
        <Link to="/about" className="text-white hover:text-purple-400">About</Link>
      </nav>
      
      <Routes>
        <Route path="/" element={<Home />} />
        <Route path="/about" element={<About />} />
      </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>
  )
}
